Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1

7roq A 1110 A 1111

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Peptide name
Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1

7roq A 54 A 626

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1

5xjy A 1359 A 1723

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1

5xjy A 1359 A 1660

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Peptide name
Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1

5xjy A 626 A 1465

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Peptide name
Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1

5xjy A 626 A 1477

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Phospholipid-transporting ATPase ABCA1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.
